name: 透
trans: ──There's a lot of them huh. In the audience seats.

name: プロデューサー
text:
あれっ、リハにお客さん入れるのか……！？
そんな話聞いて────
trans:
Wait, the audience is in for the rehearsals...?!
I didn't hear anything about tha────

name: プロデューサー
text:
──リハってさ、貴重な時間だから……
もう少し緊張感持ってやってくれたら嬉しいんだけどな？
trans:
──Look, the rehearsals are important so...
I'd appreciate it if you could have 
a little more nerves in you, you know?

name: 透
text: イメージトレーニング

name: 透
text:
席、いっぱいだから
お客さんで
trans:
The audience seats are filled you see.
With an audience.
